Represents operators satisfying the Heisenberg canonical commutation relations\
\>", "TechNoteTableText",ExpressionUUID->
     "67b5daa1-ccdd-42e2-ad77-250dc9a8ef24"]}
  }]], "DefinitionBox",
 CellID->2096742444,ExpressionUUID->"46eaaf0b-c9bb-4a86-b47b-8ae4032f82b3"],

